import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1):
    v0 = jnp.minimum(x0, x1)
    v1 = jnp.cos(x1)
    v2 = jnp.maximum(x1, x0)
    v3 = jnp.exp(x0)
    v4 = jnp.cos(x1)
    v5 = jnp.tanh(v2)
    v6 = jnp.multiply(x1, v2)
